    TxtCompress
    this class is specialized for Text file and csv(comma separated value) based on a separator, it identifies words, and do a dictionary compression by replacing these words(SOLn+xxxxx) by the index of word(SAliasn) in parallel it replace integer by an INTn symbol and an float by a FloatAscii symbol.
